<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Here are some events that we will be attending and where you can find us throughout the year.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">We can be found most weekends at the <a target="_blank" href="http://raleighfleamarket.net/"><u><strong>Raleigh Flea Market</strong></u></a> located within the State Fairgrounds at 1025 Blue Ridge Rd at Hillsborough Street in Raleigh NC 27607.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">We’re <a target="_blank" href="map.pdf"><u><strong>located</strong></u></a> near the middle of the outside area of the flea market down the center aisle. You can’t miss our bright red canopy. … and even if you do, just follow the smell of great tasting kettle corn being popped fresh. You’ll be sure to find us that way.</p>

<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">The <a target="_blank" href="http://raleighfleamarket.net/"><u><strong>Raleigh Flea Market</strong></u></a> is open all year round (except during the weeks when the State Fair is on in October) and offers some great buys on all kinds of items from a wide variety of vendors. </p>
