<p><a title="" href="http://www.warwickapplefest.com"><strong>Warwick Applefest</strong></a> 2013 in Warwick NY - Sunday October 6th, 2013 held in beautiful Warwick NY, the apple picking capital of the Hudson Valley. Sample some of the best apple pies, cakes, deserts and fresh picked apples from local orchards. Local crafts, artis and vendors of all types of items line the streets. There are also plenty of games and rides for the kids.</p>
